  "title": "Junior Commodity Trader",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>Develop and optimize automated trading programs by translating trader strategies into efficient Python code. Leverage AI tools to design intelligent trading solutions that improve decision-making and execution. Maintain system reliability and collaborate to resolve technical issues impacting trading operations.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Translate trader strategies into efficient Python code to develop automated trading programs that optimize trading performance</li><li>Design and implement AI-driven trading solutions to enhance decision-making accuracy and execution efficiency</li><li>Perform routine maintenance on trading software to ensure system reliability and optimal performance</li><li>Collaborate with team members to diagnose and resolve technical issues affecting trading operations promptly</li><li>Utilize AI tools to collect market information and generate daily summary reports to support trading activities</li><li>Monitor and analyze automated trading system performance to maximize profit and loss outcomes</li></ul><p><strong>Preferred competencies and qualifications</strong></p><ul><li>Bachelor’s Degree in Computer Science or a related field</li><li>Demonstrated programming skills with 1-2 years of relevant work experience; new graduates with strong programming capabilities are encouraged to apply</li></ul>",
